Manchester United will host Colchester Utd in the Carabao Cup quarter-final clash. The draws were conducted on Thursday morning, following the conclusion of the round of 16 fixtures on Wednesday night. Manchester United defeated Chelsea 2-1, while Liverpool won 5-4 on penalties against Arsenal on Wednesday. Fixtures for the quarter-finals will commence on December 16. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.